node.title: Kansas Jayhawks win 2022 NCAA Men's Basketball Tournament
node.description: Kansas managed to complete the largest comeback ever in the championship game.
node.content: ["The Kansas Jayhawks have won the 2022 NCAA Men's Basketball Tournament, defeating the UNC Tar Heels 72-69. This is Kansas' fourth national title, and the school's first since 2008.", "Kansas managed to complete the largest comeback ever in the championship game, trailing by 16 at one point in the first half and having gone into the break down 15."]
